node.text:
@deepak_karra 😍 posts the most beautiful and rarest birds on the planet! Which is your favorite, from 1-10? 🌎
Follow @deepak_karra if you haven’t already

The featured birds are 
1. Pink Robin 
2. Rose Robin
3. Diamond Firetail
4. Spotted Pardalote
5. Rufous Fantail 
6. Superb Fairy-Wren 
7. Australian Ringneck 
8. Rainbow Lorikeet 
9. Scarlet Robin
10. Eastern Spinebill

node.text:
The wonderland of Puga Valley in Ladakh, India via @apytravelstories 🤯 

The Puga valley in the Changthang valley lies at about 22 km to the east of the Salt Lake valley across the Polokonka La pass (5,350 m). It is famous for its borax and sulphur deposits and hot water springs.

Video by @apytravelstories
